  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nSee title.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nChosen amount and currency should be preserved in the send flow after scanning the recipient's QR code, so that user can proceed with the transaction.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nIt resets to 0.0 ETH.\r\n\r\n#### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nAmount and currency is retained after scanning the QR code.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- initiate send flow\r\n- specify an amount and select a token (e.g. 30 DAI)\r\n- choose recipient by scanning QR code\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n- Status version: **1.1.0 (!)**\r\n- Operating System: Android",
